      <abstract displayLabel="Abstract">This publication revises NIST SP 800-53 Revision 1 by adding specific
                guidance on the application of security controls to Industrial Control Systems
                (ICS). That ICS-specific guidance is contained in Appendix I, and addresses the
                following: Tailoring guidance; Security control enhancements; Supplements to the
                security control baselines; and Supplemental guidance.</abstract>
